transcript:
Customer: Phone nahi uthate.
Customer: Hello.
Customer: Hello.
Customer: 25400 de diye maine.
Executive: Bharat ji baat kar rahe hain sir?
Customer: Ha ji boliye.
Executive: Sir Adarsh baat kar raha hun IndiaMART head office se. Account manager aapka. Sir kal aapne video meeting ke liye interest theek hai abhi schedule lagaya tha main hi khol ke dekh raha.
Executive: Achcha vaise hi kiya tha.
Customer: Kuch issue aa raha hai sir services mein is time?
Customer: Na koi. Lead kam aa rahi hai sir aaj kal.
Executive: Lead kam aa rahi hai?
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: Okay sir check kar le raha hun main.
Executive: Lead aayi hui hai sir abhi achcha aapko bulk ki lead chahiye.
Customer: Hmm.
Executive: Abhi ek ghante pehle aayi hui hai plastic box ki 1000 pieces ki sir. Isme deal karte ho aap? Nahi karte hain.
Customer: Nahi.
Executive: Achcha isme nahi karte hain aap. Pipo jo flute wali sheet aati hai neele rang wali?
Customer: Haan sir.
Executive: Koi nahi aap dekh lena sir main baad mein karunga aapko call thodi der mein abhi busy hun.
Customer: Maine dekh chaliye theek hai aap free hoke call.
